---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | YourHQ"
  description="Privacy Policy for YourHQ - Our commitment to data sovereignty and security."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-bone min-h-screen font-sans text-carbon selection:bg-deepGreen selection:text-white pb-24">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mb-6">Privacy Policy</p>
        
        <h1 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-carbon mb-8">
          Privacy &amp; Data Sovereignty
        </h1>
        
        <!-- The Whisper / Tension Technique -->
        <p class="font-serif italic text-headline text-terracotta leading-snug mb-6">
          Founder-led. Transparent about where your data lives.
        </p>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-subhead text-softGrey leading-relaxed">
          We believe you should own your digital home and the data inside it. Here is how we protect that right.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE DOCUMENT -->
    <article class="px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-elegant border border-carbon/5 p-8 md:p-16 lg:p-20">
        
        <!-- Lead Statement -->
        <p class="font-sans text-subhead text-carbon leading-relaxed mb-12">
          YourHQ operates under the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020. Beyond legal compliance, our core philosophy is <strong class="font-semibold text-carbon">Data Sovereignty</strong>: We are the caretakers of your digital assets, but you remain the owner.
        </p>

        <hr class="border-t border-carbon/10 my-16" />

        <div class="space-y-16">

          <!-- 1. INFO WE COLLECT -->
          <section>
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">1.</span> Information We Collect
            </h3>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p class="mb-6">To build and maintain your website, we collect:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 pl-6 list-disc list-outside marker:text-carbon/20">
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Business Identity:</strong> Name, contact details, and business descriptions.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Website Content:</strong> Images, text, logos, and files you upload to our Shared Drive.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Voice Data:</strong> Audio recordings from your "Drive-Home Interview" with our AI agent.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Technical Data:</strong> Analytics on how your website performs.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 2. TECH STACK -->
          <section>
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">2.</span> Our Technology Stack &amp; Data Storage
            </h3>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p class="mb-8">We believe in radical transparency regarding where your data lives. We use best-in-class infrastructure to ensure speed and security.</p>
              
              <div class="border-t border-carbon/5">
                <!-- Supabase -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 sm:gap-6 items-start py-6 border-b border-carbon/5">
                  <span class="font-mono text-badge text-deepGreen sm:min-w-[120px] pt-1">Supabase:</span>
                  <span class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey">We use Supabase for our database. We implement <strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Row Level Security (RLS)</strong> policies, meaning your data is cryptographically segregated. Only authorized users (you and our admins) can access your specific records.</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Stripe -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 sm:gap-6 items-start py-6 border-b border-carbon/5">
                  <span class="font-mono text-badge text-deepGreen sm:min-w-[120px] pt-1">Stripe:</span>
                  <span class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey">We use Stripe for all payments. YourHQ never sees or stores your credit card numbers. Stripe adheres to the highest level of PCI Service Provider Level 1 standards.</span>
                </div>
                <!-- ElevenLabs -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 sm:gap-6 items-start py-6 border-b border-carbon/5">
                  <span class="font-mono text-badge text-deepGreen sm:min-w-[120px] pt-1">ElevenLabs:</span>
                  <span class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey">Used for our AI Interview Agent. Your voice data is processed solely to transcribe information for your website build. We do not use your voice to clone your identity.</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Vercel -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 sm:gap-6 items-start py-6 border-b border-carbon/5">
                  <span class="font-mono text-badge text-deepGreen sm:min-w-[120px] pt-1">Vercel:</span>
                  <span class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey">Your website files are hosted on Vercel's global edge network to ensure 99.9% uptime and lightning-fast loading speeds for your customers.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 3. DATA SOVEREIGNTY -->
          <section>
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">3.</span> Data Sovereignty (Ownership)
            </h3>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p class="mb-6">This is where we differ from platforms like Facebook or Instagram:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 pl-6 list-disc list-outside marker:text-carbon/20">
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">You own your content.</strong> We claim no intellectual property rights over the text and images you provide.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">You own your customer list.</strong> Any leads generated by your website belong 100% to you. We do not mine, sell, or share your customer data.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Portability.</strong> If you choose to leave YourHQ (after the minimum term), we provide you with a static export of your website files. We do not hold your digital presence hostage.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 4. VOICE DATA -->
          <section>
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">4.</span> How We Use Voice Data
            </h3>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p class="mb-6">When you speak with our AI Agent (Lian's Digital Voice):</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 pl-6 list-disc list-outside marker:text-carbon/20">
                <li>The conversation is recorded and transcribed to generate website copy.</li>
                <li>These recordings are stored securely within our private logs.</li>
                <li>We do not share these recordings with third parties for marketing purposes.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 5. YOUR RIGHTS -->
          <section>
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">5.</span> Your Rights
            </h3>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p class="mb-6">Under the NZ Privacy Act, you have the right to:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 pl-6 list-disc list-outside marker:text-carbon/20">
                <li>Ask for a copy of any personal information we hold about you.</li>
                <li>Ask for it to be corrected if you think it is wrong.</li>
                <li>Request that your data be deleted from our servers (subject to us needing to keep billing records for tax purposes).</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

        </div>

        <!-- CONTACT BOX -->
        <div class="mt-20 md:ml-9 bg-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-carbon/5 shadow-subtle">
          <h4 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-4">Privacy Officer Contact</h4>
          <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey mb-6">If you have any concerns about data security or wish to exercise your rights:</p>
          
          <div class="font-sans text-ui text-carbon space-y-2">
            <p class="font-semibold">YourHQ Limited</p>
            <p class="text-softGrey">Email: <a href="mailto:lian@yourhq.co.nz" class="text-carbon hover:text-signal transition-colors underline decoration-carbon/20 underline-offset-4">lian@yourhq.co.nz</a></p>
            <p class="text-softGrey">Phone: <a href="sms:0275668803" class="text-carbon hover:text-signal transition-colors underline decoration-carbon/20 underline-offset-4">027 566 8803</a></p>
            <p class="text-softGrey">Northland, New Zealand</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FOOTER / SIGN OFF -->
        <div class="border-t border-carbon/10 mt-16 pt-8 font-mono text-badge text-softGrey md:pl-9">
          <p>Last updated: May 2026</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>